<a name= "passwd"></a>
<h2>9.3 - linux ($B$"$k$$$O$=$NB>(B System-7 $B7A<0(B) $B$N%Q%9%o!<%I%U%!%$%k$r(B
BSD-$B7A<0$KJQ49$9$k$K$O(B</h2>

<p>
$B$^$:!"(BLinux $B%Q%9%o!<%I$,%7%c%I!<2=$5$l$F$$$k$+$I$&$+$rD4$Y$F$/$@@$5$$!#(B
$B$b$7!"%7%c%I!<2=$5$l$F$$$^$7$?$i!"(B<a href="http://www.openwall.com/john/">John the Ripper</a>
$BIUB0$N(B unshadow $B%f!<%F%#%j%F%#$G!"(B<tt>passwd</tt> $B$H(B <tt>shadow</tt> $B%U%!%$%k(B
$B$H$r%^!<%8$7$F!"$R$H$D$N(B System 7-$B7A<0$N%U%!%$%k$K$7$F$/$@@$5$$!#(B

<p>
Linux $B$N%Q%9%o!<%I%U%!%$%k$O!"$3$3$G$O(B <tt>linux_passwd</tt> $B$H8F$V$3$H$K$7$^$9!#(B
$B$3$l$K$O%U%#!<%k%I(B 4 $B$H(B 7 $B$H$N4V$K(B ::0:0 $B$rDI2C$9$kI,MW$,$"$j$^$9!#$3$l$O!"(B
<a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=awk&amp;sektion=1">awk(1)</a>
$B$,<+F0E*$K<B9T$7$F$/$l$^$9!#(B

<blockquote>
<pre>
# <b>cat linux_passwd | awk -F : '{printf("%s:%s:%s:%s::0:0:%s:%s:%s\n", \</b>
> <b>$1,$2,$3,$4,$5,$6,$7); }' &gt; new_passwd</b>
</pre>
</blockquote>

$B$3$N;~E@@$G!"(B<tt>new_passwd</tt> $B%U%!%$%k$rJQ99$7$F!"(B root $B$J$I$N%7%9%F%`4XO"$N(B
$B%(%s%H%j$G!"4{$K(B OpenBSD $B$N%Q%9%o!<%I%U%!%$%k$KB8:_$7$F$$$?$j!"(BOpenBSD $B$G$O(B
$BL50UL#$J$b$N(B ($B$9$Y$F(B) $B$r:o=|$7$F$*$$$F$/$@@$5$$!#$5$i$K(B <tt>new_passwd</tt> $B$H(B
OpenBSD $BB&$N(B <tt>/etc/passwd</tt> $B$G%f!<%6L>$d%f!<%6(B ID $B$N=EJ#$,$J$$$3$H$b(B
$B3N$+$a$F$/$@@$5$$!#$3$l$r<B;\$9$k$N$K$$$A$P$s4JC1$JJ}K!$O!"(B
$B$^$C$5$i$J(B <tt>/etc/passwd</tt> $B$+$i;O$a$k$3$H$G$9!#(B

<blockquote>
<pre>
# <b>cat new_passwd &gt;&gt; /etc/master.passwd</b>
# <b>pwd_mkdb -p /etc/master.passwd</b>
</pre>
</blockquote>

$B:G8e$N%9%F%C%W$H$7$F!"(B/etc/spwd.db $B$H(B /etc/pwd.db $B%U%!%$%k$r:n@@.$7$J$*$9$N$K(B
<tt>pwd_mkdb</tt> $B$,I,MW$K$J$j$^$9!#$3$l$O$^$?(B System 7-$B7A<0$N%Q%9%o!<%I(B
$B%U%!%$%k(B ($B0E9f2=$5$l$?%Q%9%o!<%I$O=|$/(B) $B$r(B /etc/passwd $B$K:n$j$^$9!#$3$l$r(B
$B;HMQ$9$k%W%m%0%i%`$,$"$k$+$i$G$9!#(BOpenBSD $B$O%Q%9%o!<%I$K:G$b6/NO$J0E9f(B
blowfish $B$r;HMQ$7$F$$$F!"$3$l$O40A4$J(B System 7-$B7A<0$N%Q%9%o!<%I%U%!%$%k$r(B
$B;HMQ$9$k%7%9%F%`$G$O$^$:8+$k$3$H$,$G$-$^$;$s!#$3$N6/NO$J0E9fJ}<0$K@@Z$jBX$($k(B
$B$N$G$7$?$i!"3F%f!<%6$K(B 'passwd' $B$r<B9T$7$F$b$i$$!"%Q%9%o!<%I$rJQ$($F$b$i$$(B
$B$^$7$g$&!#$_$s$J$,F~$l$k?7$7$$%Q%9%o!<%I$O!"%G%U%)%k%H@@_Dj$N0E9f2=J}<0$G(B
$B0E9f2=$5$l$^$9(B
(/etc/login.conf $B$rJQ99$7$F$$$J$1$l$P!"DL>o$O(B blowfish $B$G$9(B)$B!#(B
$B$^$?$O(B root $B$K$J$C$F(B <tt>passwd <i>username</i></tt> $B$r<B9T$7$F$bNI$$$G$7$g$&!#(B


<p>
<a name= "Interact"></a>
<h2>9.4 - OpenBSD $B>e$G(B Linux $B%P%$%J%j$r<B9T$9$k$K$O(B</h2>

<p>
OpenBSD/i386 $B$O!"%+!<%M%k$,(B COMPAT_LINUX $B%*%W%7%g%sIU$-$G%3%s%Q%$%k$5$l!"(B
sysctl $B$N<B9T;~%Q%i%a!<%?(B kern.emul.linux $B$,@@_Dj$5$l$F$$$k>l9g$K!"(B
Linux $B%P%$%J%j$r<B9T$9$k$3$H$,$G$-$^$9!#(B
($B$"$J$?$,;HMQ$9$Y$-(B) GENERIC $B%+!<%M%k$r;HMQ$7$F$$$k>l9g$K$O!"(BCOMPAT_LINUX
$B$O4{$KM-8z2=$5$l$F$$$^$9$N$G!"$"$J$?$OC1$K0J2<$N$h$&$K$9$k$@@$1$G$9!#(B

<blockquote>
<pre>
# <b>sysctl -w kern.emul.linux=1</b>
</pre>
</blockquote>

$B%3%s%T%e!<%?$N5/F0;~$K$3$l$,<+F0E*$K<B9T$5$l$k$h$&$K$9$k$?$a$K$O!"(B
$B0J2<$N(B /etc/sysctl.conf $B%U%!%$%k$N(B

<blockquote>
<pre>
#kern.emul.linux=1      # enable running Linux binaries
</pre>
</blockquote>

$B9TF,$N(B # ($B%3%a%s%H(B) $BJ8;z$r=|5n$7$F0J2<$N$h$&$K$7!"(B

<blockquote>
<pre>
kern.emul.linux=1       # enable running Linux binaries
</pre>
</blockquote>

$B$=$7$F$3$l$rH?1G$9$k$?$a!":F5/F0$7$F$/$@@$5$$!#(B

<p>
$B%9%?%F%#%C%/%j%s%/$5$l$F$$$J$$(B Linux $B%P%$%J%j(B
($B$D$^$j$[$H$s$I(B) $B$r<B9T$9$k$?$a$K$O!"(B
<a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=compat_linux&amp;sektion=8">compat_linux(8)</a>
$B%^%K%e%"%k%Z!<%8$K5-=R$5$l$?<j=g$K=>$&I,MW$,$"$j$^$9!#(B

<p>
$BJXMx$J(B Linux $B%i%$%V%i%j$N$[$H$s$I$r4JC1$K<hF@@$9$k$?$a$NJ}K!$O!"(Bports
$B%3%l%/%7%g%s$+$i(B <tt>redhat/base</tt> $B$r%$%s%9%H!<%k$9$k$3$H$G$9!#(B
ports $B%3%l%/%7%g%s$K$D$$$F$N$h$j>\$7$$$3$H$O(B
<a href="faq8.html#Ports">FAQ 8 - Ports</a> $B$r;2>H$7$F$/$@@$5$$!#(B
ports $B%D%j!<$,%$%s%9%H!<%k$5$l$F$$$k$N$G$7$?$i!"(B
$B<!$N%3%^%s%I$G(B Linux $B%i%$%V%i%j$r%$%s%9%H!<%k$G$-$^$9!#(B

<blockquote>
<pre>
# <b>cd /usr/ports/emulators/redhat/base</b>
# <b>make install</b>
</pre>
</blockquote>


<p>
<a name= "Ext2FS"></a>
<h2>9.5 - OpenBSD $B$+$i(B Linux $B$N%U%!%$%k$K%"%/%;%9$9$k$K$O(B</h2>

<p>
OpenBSD $B$O(B EXT2FS $B%U%!%$%k%7%9%F%`$r%5%]!<%H$7$F$$$^$9!#(BOpenBSD $B$,(B Linux $B%Q!<%F%#%7%g%s$r$I$N$h$&$K8+$F$$$k$N$+!"(B

<blockquote>
<pre>
# <b>disklabel <i>disk</i></b>
</pre>
</blockquote>

($B$3$3$G(B <tt><b><i>disk</i></b></tt> $B$O!"$"$J$?$N%G%#%9%/$N%G%P%$%9L>$N$3$H$G!"(B 
$B$?$H$($P!"(B<tt><b>wd0</b></tt>)
$B$r;HMQ$7$FCN$k$3$H$,$G$-$^$9!#(B
$B$7$+$7!"$=$l$,$I$N$h$&$JJQ99$G$"$C$F$b!"(B
<a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=disklabel&amp;sektion=8">disklabel (8)</a> 
$B$d(B
<a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=fdisk&amp;sektion=8">fdisk (8)</a> 
$B$r%G%#%9%/%i%Y%k$rJQ99$9$k$?$a$K(B<b>$B;HMQ$7$F$O$$$1$^$;$s(B</b>$B!#(B

<p>
disklabel $B$N;HMQ$K$D$$$F!">\$7$/$O(B
<a href="faq14.html#disklabel">FAQ 14 - disklabel</a> $B$r;2>H$7$F$/$@@$5$$!#(B



